Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.79,0:00:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭{\c&H0000E1&}囃{\c&HFFFFFF&}篇 其一\N三四
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.66,0:01:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前头叶？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是一篇论文 说有一种特别的寄生虫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能感染作为大脑一部分的前头叶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上存在着无数的寄生生物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候能控制宿主的生活 这点广为人知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 寄生于人体并控制宿主的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被坚决否决了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制人类就意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就能控制人类的感情 也就是思想了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制思想？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一个人的思想是寄生虫的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就如同黑死病一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 思想会变成不可治疗的传染病一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这思想一旦扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会成为种族歧视或宗教歧视下大规模虐杀的论调
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以脑内寄生虫的论调在战后便消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 脑内寄生虫一定存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 爷爷你会证明给人看的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是打算朝这目标努力的...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在假设还存在的时候都没能证明的科学家为数众多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 要是我的研究获得正当的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那即使身体早已入土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会有人唤醒我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒？像神一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 爷爷我就成为神了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为神？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果...果然是一把只能打开鸡窝的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧 回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理子 别急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是拿这把钥匙打开的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你试过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙没错 只是太硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理子 有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用这把钥匙打开过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试过的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开它 就能获得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能和这地狱说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理子 有人来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点送进去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边先等等 从这里开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈在哪 在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美代子 听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈都在战争中失去了所有亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 如果爸爸死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有人照顾你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果爸爸死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去找高野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:06:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高野一二三老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去他那里试试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高野一二三？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 高野老师是爸爸的恩师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会帮助你...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生 突发状况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 快进行手术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能照顾你的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高野一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的人 亲戚之类的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么你这都做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱之家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 但说这是好方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里 浪费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃 你敢留下一点看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山那边的孤儿院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里还有吃点心的时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院长是个很和蔼可亲的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都叫她妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了 这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去有妈妈的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有机会 大家会逃跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃得出去的话 当然想逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定会被抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃不出去的 门锁着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 到处都锁着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一把
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中庭鸡窝的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和楼梯后面那扇门的钥匙是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理子 难道你用这把钥匙...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人当然危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果大家在一起 就会有点不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说过去有人集中逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他们保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但听说那时被抓住的 只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道为什么只有一个人被抓住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们全都分散逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 要不要试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也害怕 要是被抓住 肯定会被杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们想永远呆在这儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 我不要 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是唯一一次的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要唯一一次的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美代子你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能逃掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能保证
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:11:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你一起来的话 比我一个人的成功概率更高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然对你来说也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 美代子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们在那干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 按照预订的 分散向不同方向跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把我的手指...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指手指手指
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的厚恩我不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱嘛 就应该给人生路还长的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了年纪的人留着也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真羡慕高野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么好的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在那个世界一定很自豪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没能让他自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成祖父研究的那一刻 我第一次受到了祖父的赞扬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三四你努力到今天 不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽你所能到处送礼 得到了众人的信任和指示
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把这些钱交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:14:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就意味着我认同你为高野研究的正式继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 对您表示由衷的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我最后什么都没能帮到他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这也算是我对高野的一种赎罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想祖父拥有很好的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我黑色的眼睛里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你的研究受到任何玷污
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是发生什么事 就随时来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会倾力相助的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的研究经过数十年一直沉睡着...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说这研究在军队上层也几乎无人问津
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此无人知晓 导致无法获得经营资金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛高野老师借用了你的身体完成了研究
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许真的没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也感觉到了奇妙的因缘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰野小姐 请不要误解哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这研究的目的不是为了拥有细菌武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了其危险性而防患于未然的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 理事会有几个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一是将研究费交给研究领域拥有优秀才能的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我回嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认为除了我之外还有谁熟悉此项研究吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 鹰野小姐 这里先息怒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然这里我们会搞得让你好办的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此话怎讲？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位人物的选择 是我控制的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰野小姐你只要选择容易合伙的人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是鹰野小姐你的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概地位会是副队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计你就是少校了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不错啊 鹰野少校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是鹰野少校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 这位是入江京介医生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您...您好 我是入江
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用怕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:17:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我参加雏见泽综合症的治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我十分吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止世上无人解明的神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法抑制知识上的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像入江医生这样经验丰富的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意委身到乡下地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我可以的话 请一定要让我加入
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 入江所长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰野小姐 给你介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两位是富竹和小此木
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我是富竹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被任命为此次计划的监查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小此木
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是非正规部队之一——“野狗”的队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常驻雏见泽 直接支援少校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把你当成是保镖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为少校的手足 请随意差遣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边没有 去那边找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神你这坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要我遭这样的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸说过 人生分好和坏两种
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一个都不会持久的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这也不会持久的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样结束我的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指引我走向和之前不幸所相应的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这也做不到 那我不要这样的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这雷杀死我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田无美代子就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你夺走我的父母一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就在此夺走我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.13,0:22:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 有什么动向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.81,0:23:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才岐阜来定时联系了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也说没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.15,0:23:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久那讨厌的记忆和可恶的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.95,0:23:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会成为我和爷爷的历史的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.68,0:23:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上一集成为话题的“哇哇”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太想提及的问题...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.43,0:23:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了过去爸爸珍藏的录像带后我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.70,0:23:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底看了什么录像带啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.76,0:24:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金发的哥哥姐姐在车里摔跤的录像带
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.45,0:24:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 祭囃 其二
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.60,0:24:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢动
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.25,0:24:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨花.
